cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.NI, cs.CR 

This paper focuses on benchmarking distributed stream processing engines, which involves aspects of distributed computing (cs.DC), database systems (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), networked systems (cs.NI), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, the emphasis on measuring the performance of these systems suggests that cs.DC and cs.DB are the most likely sub-categories.
